gn view...\" state. The recovery is to close the window and reopen the design view. This matches what's in the knowledge file exactly.\n\nLooking at the structure, the source has one main heading with the RST `--` style, and the knowledge file appropriately has one section to capture this content. The section text is substantial enough at well over 50 characters.\n\nFor the hints, I'm checking whether they contain technical identifiers like PascalCase class names, annotations, or exception names—they don't. The provided hints (設計書ビュー, 画面項目一覧, 業務画面JSP, 画面項目定義作成, システム機能設計書, 設計書ビューを開く) are fitting for this content. Since `no_knowledge_content` is false, I can skip that validation. Everything checks out—the knowledge file is clean with all source content preserved, no fabrications, appropriate sections, and adequate hints.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12902,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":12902,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a00c761a-d71c-485b-b31c-3a0dd0d4d8f8","uuid":"7fcd09c0-5baf-4fa8-a2a7-d4eba6453d0a"}
